==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Spark coil
<hw>Spark coil</hw>. <fld>(Elec.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>An induction
coil used for producing sparks, esp. in an internal-combustion engine,
wireless telegraph apparatus, etc.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A
self-induction coil used to increase the spark in an electric
gas-lighting apparatus.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sparker</ent>⟦br⟧
